{"tid":2073602,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我老豆成日掉人野，仲點同佢慶祝父親節","createTime":"2020-06-21T12:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T07:30:01.000Z","uid":280613,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e7293efcff38f33f5b0ada6e961e998aac56d2e1","tid":2073602,"uid":280613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:38:56.000Z","msg":"有點長，但希望比意見<br />\n<br />\n我老豆已退休<br />\n求其有一樣壞習慣都死<br />\n但佢就乜都有<br />\n<br />\n由細到大，鐘意掉我啲漫畫、雜誌、玩具<br />\n而家就連我食開嘅辣椒醬都掉<br />\n<br />\n因為習慣，食飯一定分開煮/食<br />\n<br />\n衞生編<br />\n<br />\n佢每朝都會好多痰、口水、鼻水鼻涕係個廁所四圍申，唔會用紙巾，早午晚三餐餐後又係咁，有時仲會係廚房申，佢每次用完我地都要消毒至咁用<br />\n<br />\n佢有香港腳，好撚臭，拖鞋一陣臭屎味，佢有兩對拖鞋，屋內屋外各一對，街坊行過都話臭....有次隻屎虫飛左去佢拖鞋，都臭到反肚<br />\n同佢講，發脾四、鬧交....買左支野比佢噴，又唔噴...<br />\n<br />\n生活編<br />\n<br />\n我住井字公屋，佢成日會出去行，鬆一鬆腳<br />\n以前熱愛吸煙，一日行無數咁多轉，街坊屌過佢幾次，之後戒左<br />\n但煙癮起，成日要出去街，但好鐘意開住個鐵閘、有時去完街返到黎，第一時間入廚房整自己餸，閘...最後先關，有時仲入左房睇電呀，我試好多次，我入左屋去埋廁所，佢都唔撚知...<br />\n話佢...果輪就會關，過一排又係咁...<br />\n暫時我屋企仲未被老笠，已經非常好彩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我老母最近冇工開，日日兩老對住，好惡頂"},{"pid":"1854b9406fbc63644b47cf6cdaa04de9d1bc7fe9","tid":2073602,"uid":20914,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"咪唔慶祝囉"},{"pid":"c07de8e91f1168e10cbf04460f337c763cf42cdf","tid":2073602,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"換鎖"},{"pid":"e566f97e265f4ba7bf6a04ee064d31e9271c80c5","tid":2073602,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:04:06.000Z","msg":"巴打做我男朋友<br />\n同我住私樓就唔洗對住個廢老"},{"pid":"4de4b0e5552cef2ce566e4e1913ac2a2a6665408","tid":2073602,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:04:36.000Z","msg":"斷絕"},{"pid":"55734833c2242e9496a09b657c80c5664a1dea10","tid":2073602,"uid":231234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:05:48.000Z","msg":"I know that feel,bro.<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f909458ed9527574deb3c0d4e28edbb19cfb4d","tid":2073602,"uid":38891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:06:42.000Z","msg":"元寶蠟燭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff5f1d844f67193e8ea29216fb5cd77bdbe928b","tid":2073602,"uid":280613,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"e566f97e265f4ba7bf6a04ee064d31e9271c80c5","tid":2073602,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:04:06.000Z","msg":"巴打做我男朋友<br />\n同我住私樓就唔洗對住個廢老"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:16:03.000Z","msg":"定叫我老豆搬去你度住"},{"pid":"0eaded56635726db5efe66c2bdefa63d6d1cd2d7","tid":2073602,"uid":280613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c07de8e91f1168e10cbf04460f337c763cf42cdf","tid":2073602,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"換鎖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:16:37.000Z","msg":"話曬一家人"},{"pid":"c7127bb25a85641f25e769ff0d5e14980455236e","tid":2073602,"uid":39515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0eaded56635726db5efe66c2bdefa63d6d1cd2d7","tid":2073602,"uid":280613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c07de8e91f1168e10cbf04460f337c763cf42cdf","tid":2073602,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"換鎖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:16:37.000Z","msg":"話曬一家人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:18:14.000Z","msg":"係囉 話曬一家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca45ae1de7f908c38ea8a2a7a71649cf751dfe67","tid":2073602,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:19:05.000Z","msg":"掉佢落街慶祝"},{"pid":"8130555bc4b3638e4a3bf053c24172c790b38c94","tid":2073602,"uid":280613,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:21:03.000Z","msg":"後補<br />\n<br />\n佢本時煮嘅野食都好臭<br />\n<br />\n咸魚臭到仆街，佢專買啲平價野<br />\n專鐘意食臭野<br />\n有次我地一家食醬油蟹，佢就話啲肉又梅又臭<br />\n<br />\n煮完唔啱食就倒倒倒....<br />\n一個食，煮二人份量，食唔曬<br />\n又倒...<br />\n<br />\n大佬柴米油鹽樣樣都係錢....我地係咁慳，佢就係嘥..."},{"pid":"1bf2e4336c31010e5f80af60ffbde368f718e132","tid":2073602,"uid":280613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca45ae1de7f908c38ea8a2a7a71649cf751dfe67","tid":2073602,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:19:05.000Z","msg":"掉佢落街慶祝"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"有諗過....但有時又過唔到自己果關<br />\n因為我識專重別人"},{"pid":"4b23a5976908e6e6ae508968237886108986f953","tid":2073602,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1bf2e4336c31010e5f80af60ffbde368f718e132","tid":2073602,"uid":280613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca45ae1de7f908c38ea8a2a7a71649cf751dfe67","tid":2073602,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:19:05.000Z","msg":"掉佢落街慶祝"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"有諗過....但有時又過唔到自己果關<br />\n因為我識專重別人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:24:31.000Z","msg":"首先都要佢值得尊重"},{"pid":"480790c8ee8167a0806427232630091abb66158d","tid":2073602,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:34:23.000Z","msg":"打7佢"},{"pid":"7bdeaa2583eb78700428842a0920af9c26e3143a","tid":2073602,"uid":58852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:45:03.000Z","msg":"聽落佢唔係性格問題<br />\n主要係衛生問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔死得人嘅<br />\n快趣搵錢搬出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259f9188471a81b17da0b7b8273a351855ca9698","tid":2073602,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ff5f1d844f67193e8ea29216fb5cd77bdbe928b","tid":2073602,"uid":280613,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"e566f97e265f4ba7bf6a04ee064d31e9271c80c5","tid":2073602,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:04:06.000Z","msg":"巴打做我男朋友<br />\n同我住私樓就唔洗對住個廢老"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:16:03.000Z","msg":"定叫我老豆搬去你度住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"你黎啦<br />\n比你過好啲嘅生活"},{"pid":"39bf800a1bad9c6232f0c201ee0b21249e2cc846","tid":2073602,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:20:49.000Z","msg":"拿拿臨搬出去住保平安   活得更舒暢  更有尊嚴<br />\n<br />\n唔太搵到錢都住個劏房頂住先"},{"pid":"0fdc78f93d7241bce3e989a9d25ccdd08c83db29","tid":2073602,"uid":132703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:22:03.000Z","msg":"點解當初你老母會肯同佢一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada18ea3c366244f88176068136c00e1d36de26a","tid":2073602,"uid":117780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T17:02:31.000Z","msg":"算好,我屋企個件賭錢十幾年 輸身家<br />\n小小野就發脾氣 打交,話佢兩句,衝過黎打我<br />\n係佢眼中無其他人,咁既情況過左十幾廿年"},{"pid":"169e9cee9f91516d77aaf5ef4d376adb99dd38b4","tid":2073602,"uid":280613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0fdc78f93d7241bce3e989a9d25ccdd08c83db29","tid":2073602,"uid":132703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:22:03.000Z","msg":"點解當初你老母會肯同佢一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T01:05:57.000Z","msg":"都係果句<br />\n我老母以前有個好好嘅追佢，佢唔受<br />\n揀左呢個"},{"pid":"6629c95fdc6649c025304e2c4d2e6f44d6d91e80","tid":2073602,"uid":280613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ada18ea3c366244f88176068136c00e1d36de26a","tid":2073602,"uid":117780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T17:02:31.000Z","msg":"算好,我屋企個件賭錢十幾年 輸身家<br />\n小小野就發脾氣 打交,話佢兩句,衝過黎打我<br />\n係佢眼中無其他人,咁既情況過左十幾廿年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T01:07:30.000Z","msg":"你果個衰到極，你地可以去得好盡對佢唔駛心軟都得<br />\n我果個又衰唔曬，但又唔係好果種"},{"pid":"2cec6e1a2248b71a9081a230cc7c740c01fadcfe","tid":2073602,"uid":117780,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6629c95fdc6649c025304e2c4d2e6f44d6d91e80","tid":2073602,"uid":280613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ada18ea3c366244f88176068136c00e1d36de26a","tid":2073602,"uid":117780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T17:02:31.000Z","msg":"算好,我屋企個件賭錢十幾年 輸身家<br />\n小小野就發脾氣 打交,話佢兩句,衝過黎打我<br />\n係佢眼中無其他人,咁既情況過左十幾廿年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T01:07:30.000Z","msg":"你果個衰到極，你地可以去得好盡對佢唔駛心軟都得<br />\n我果個又衰唔曬，但又唔係好果種"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T01:46:50.000Z","msg":"我要講既話,可以寫一萬字黎形容尼件垃圾,講唔完,根本數唔到一個優點<br />\n佢既一生只有 屌人 打交(打足我25年) 偷人地野(小米,錢,八達通),賭錢<br />\n係佢眼中只有人地錯,佢只要識少少野 拎到少少著數就一味叫囂 開心一日<br />\n但佢自己唔見左張八達通 就屌黎屌去屌足半日.<br />\n你話張子強係大賊做大事,我寫個服字,我屋企個件?連賊,廢老都不如<br />\n日日係屋企開著個VCD機食住口煙睇抗日戰爭 屙屎屙尿唔沖廁 全屋都臭到死 係出面走朗等lift都聞到臭味.<br />\n日日係到埋怨我點解教佢用智能手機.大佬智能手機出左十幾年<br />\n你等到第十年,先拎人地爛左既小米黎用,尼D思維點會識用?<br />\n你教佢用一個app,佢永遠只用一個APP,下一頁跟著點用,佢已經唔識.完全唔會學識,同埋根本唔想同佢講野.<br />\n到最後仲打電話去佢鄉下D廢老親戚訴苦 話生個仆街仔無撚用 生個不孝子出黎.講兩講又想沖過黎打我.<br />\n總之要講既 咁多年既野 不能盡錄,只能講 非常辛苦 .慘過拎綜援,慘過出生無父無母。就算講比人聽,只回應一句  你要好好對你上一代既人"},{"pid":"473b992cba4d6a0a47552649c050aa844e5f8f7a","tid":2073602,"uid":356078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:13:00.000Z","msg":"唔知點解身邊大部人的老豆都好乞人憎, 希望大家老左唔好變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200f50952f392ff241214e0938ec8465ca5977af","tid":2073602,"uid":186755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:45:20.000Z","msg":"我老豆又係好撚鐘意掉我d野<br />\n岩岩過撚完個冬天就捍我d涼鞋<br />\n話:你都唔著架啦<br />\n我dllm 冬天著乜撚野涼鞋呀<br />\nd野放係到唔郁好似得撚罪左佢咁,乜撚都鐘意掉<br />\n又唔掉埋自己出街"}]}